{"type": "article", "id": 13933, "title": "橄榄仿生外包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-25T07:33:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104228F5aYjxBfHiXmLUbP.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在黎巴嫩，每年品质最为上乘的橄榄会被摘下，做成最高品质的橄榄油，据了解，这些高品质的橄榄从采摘到冷榨整个过程一气呵成，用时不超过六个小时，每年限量生产一次。最近，Marios Karystios 为这种高质量橄榄油设计了一款专用的包装，采用橄榄形状的陶瓷瓶，经过多次复杂精密的数学计算得出最适宜存储的容量，形状和倾倒角度，是一件优秀的仿生外包装作品。<a href=\"http://www.karystios.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看设计师的更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141600Ady3pErOnb42JYkG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141600xDL1Qf3MEBKwtovT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416000nHjp1T7FxVb3l6U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416018HDqTfsMNJl0zUvS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80440098\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141602nvIb70mUtWgpjNd8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416028L4leV3KFUmP9AOr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141603Zj2rq5WFsd0e4ChK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141603lyEpF6TveQbctHL3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48655257\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141604s6NWEvx5TfUcQod0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141605djao8VWUzbm9qilk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67848411\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}